title: Ascentive Library Installer
description:
If your operating system is missing a library file needed for your Ascentive programs to function, you might get an error report, or you might see an error message like these: 
[filename].DLL or [filename].ocx or one of its dependencies is not correctly registered: a file is missing or invalid.


The File [filename].DLL or [filename].ocx is out of date or missing. This program requires a new version. 
SOLUTION: 
In order to fix this problem, you&#039;ll need to set up and register the library file. 

The easiest way to do that is to download the following file that will install and register most of the Library Files used by Ascentive&#039;s products
